"'''Shazam!'''" is a song written by [[Duane Eddy]] and [[Lee Hazlewood]] and performed by Eddy.<ref>[http://www.45cat.com/record/1151us2 Duane Eddy, "Shazam!" single release] Retrieved April 26, 2014</ref>  The song reached #4 on the [[UK Singles Chart]] and #45 on the [[Billboard Hot 100|''Billboard'' Hot 100]] in 1960.<ref>[http://www.musicvf.com/song.php?title=Shazam!+by+Duane+Eddy&id=13105 Duane Eddy, "Shazam!" Chart Positions] Retrieved April 26, 2014</ref>

==Other versions==
*[[The Shadows]] released a version of the song in [[1963 in music|1963]] as the [[A-Side and B-Side|B-side]] to their single "Geronimo".<ref>[http://www.45cat.com/record/db7163 The Shadows, "Geronimo" single release] Retrieved April 26, 2014</ref>

